snippet.title: Elleros Origins: Wytchsun trailer
snippet.description:
Elleros Origins: Wytchsun is a single-player role-playing video game developed by Rampage Interactive.

It is the first installment in the Elleros action/adventure RPG fantasy video game series. The game was announced on April 25, 2019 at the Midlands Game Awards in Birmingham, with a release date of 2020. It features Fireside AI, along with Fireside games-master, to help enhance player experience and quests.
